<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 02:15:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尽管信用评级被下调，以色列外长斯莫特里奇仍选择不与财政部高级官员会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/despite-rating-downgrade-israeli-fm-smotrich-chooses-not-to-meet-with-top-treasury-staff/0000018d-9a34-dc01-a9cf-9a7dfb4d0000</link><description>相反，财政部长参加了对陆军朱利斯基地的参观。内塔尼亚胡迄今为止尚未宣布任何计划就评级行动进行讨论</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 22:13:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/despite-rating-downgrade-israeli-fm-smotrich-chooses-not-to-meet-with-top-treasury-staff/0000018d-9a34-dc01-a9cf-9a7dfb4d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟将推进有争议的军队草案法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-coalition-to-advance-controversial-army-draft-bill/0000018d-99f7-dc01-a9cf-9bff1d670000</link><description>该法案可能在大约两周内获得议会批准，旨在延长义务兵役和预备役兵役，并提高预备役军人的豁免年龄，但不会改变给予极端正统正统派男性的豁免年龄</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 22:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-coalition-to-advance-controversial-army-draft-bill/0000018d-99f7-dc01-a9cf-9bff1d670000</guid></item><item><title>拜登敦促内塔尼亚胡制定“可靠”计划，在以色列进攻之前保护拉法的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/biden-tells-netanyahu-israel-must-have-credible-plan-to-protect-palestinians-in-rafah/0000018d-99ae-dc01-a9cf-9befa6210000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡指示以色列军队起草计划，在军事入侵之前疏散目前在拉法寻求庇护的近100万巴勒斯坦平民。两位领导人还讨论了与哈马斯达成人质协议的持续努力</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 21:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/biden-tells-netanyahu-israel-must-have-credible-plan-to-protect-palestinians-in-rafah/0000018d-99ae-dc01-a9cf-9befa6210000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨在民调中大幅领先内塔尼亚胡；目前的联盟面临失去多数席位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/gantz-holds-wide-lead-over-netanyahu-in-polls-current-coalition-faces-majority-loss/0000018d-99ac-d92c-a9ed-fbfd78510000</link><description>在以色列新闻媒体进行的两次民意调查中，甘茨领导的民族团结党获得 37 个席位，内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团获得 18 个席位</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 21:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/gantz-holds-wide-lead-over-netanyahu-in-polls-current-coalition-faces-majority-loss/0000018d-99ac-d92c-a9ed-fbfd78510000</guid></item><item><title>法院在认罪协议中判定管道公司污染以色列自然保护区有罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/court-convicts-pipeline-company-in-plea-deal-for-polluting-israeli-nature-reserve/0000018d-9975-d92c-a9ed-fbfdc0510000</link><description>该公司和两名公司官员被判对造成“该国历史上最大的生态灾难之一”的石油泄漏负责。这些罪行可能会被判处最高三年的监禁，但协议要求仅处以罚款</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 19:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/court-convicts-pipeline-company-in-plea-deal-for-polluting-israeli-nature-reserve/0000018d-9975-d92c-a9ed-fbfdc0510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院驳回允许在以色列国防军基地食用 Chametz 的请愿书，裁定侵犯权利“相当轻微”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-brushes-off-petition-to-allow-eating-chametz-on-idf-bases/0000018d-9975-d92c-a9ed-fbfd0e520000</link><description>法官们决定不干预以色列国防军的命令；判决强调军队承诺不搜查士兵的装备，这让请愿者感到“安慰”。他们说，“以色列国防军否认存在这些安排，但它们是请愿书的主要动机”</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 19:29:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-brushes-off-petition-to-allow-eating-chametz-on-idf-bases/0000018d-9975-d92c-a9ed-fbfd0e520000</guid></item><item><title>高风险：据报道摩洛哥大麻经销商抵制以色列，引用巴勒斯坦人的苦难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/high-stakes-moroccan-hashish-dealers-boycott-israel-citing-palestinian-suffering/0000018d-98dd-d92c-a9ed-fbfd9a030000</link><description>尽管向以色列出口大麻对摩洛哥的经销商来说利润丰厚，但他们不再愿意向以色列经销商出售大麻：“当我们的巴勒斯坦兄弟遭受饥饿时，为什么以色列人能够靠卖摩洛哥大麻谋生呢？”</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 18:56:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/high-stakes-moroccan-hashish-dealers-boycott-israel-citing-palestinian-suffering/0000018d-98dd-d92c-a9ed-fbfd9a030000</guid></item><item><title>拜登有一周的时间需要忘记，但内塔尼亚胡应该记住他的一些事情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/biden-had-a-week-to-forget-but-theres-something-netanyahu-should-remember-about-him/0000018d-98f5-dc01-a9cf-9afd98ef0000</link><description>美国媒体无视特朗普的失态和无知，却关注拜登的年龄和错误。因此，当美国总统称以色列在加沙的军事行动“太过分”时，许多人很快将其视为另一个错误。但拜登说出了他的真实想法</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 18:42:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/biden-had-a-week-to-forget-but-theres-something-netanyahu-should-remember-about-him/0000018d-98f5-dc01-a9cf-9afd98ef0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 128 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-128/0000018d-9943-d92c-a9ed-fbfbeb7b0000</link><description>据报道，埃及警告哈马斯，在以色列国防军拉法之前，它有两周时间与以色列达成停火协议，但埃及还威胁称，如果以色列向以色列发动地面进攻，将暂停与以色列的和平条约。 哈马斯高级官员：对拉法的任何袭击都将结束人质谈判释放协议 ■ 巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯飞往卡塔尔，与总理阿勒萨尼讨论战后加沙的前景 ■ 战争结束 128 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 17:47:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-128/0000018d-9943-d92c-a9ed-fbfbeb7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属向国际刑事法院提出针对哈马斯领导人的索赔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-lodge-claim-against-hamas-leaders-to-intl-criminal-court/0000018d-98de-dc01-a9cf-9affceb50000</link><description>已获释的人质以及仍被关押在加沙的人质亲属将飞往海牙，在国际刑事法院提供此案证词，该法院部分寻求对哈马斯领导人发出逮捕令</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 17:15:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-lodge-claim-against-hamas-leaders-to-intl-criminal-court/0000018d-98de-dc01-a9cf-9affceb50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者建立西岸前哨基地；其他人在另一起事件中袭击巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-erect-west-bank-outpost-others-attack-palestinians-in-separate-incident/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfb721d0000</link><description>以色列国防消息来源怀疑政府是否会撤离建在国家控制土地上的前哨基地 ■ 大约 15 名以色列人袭击了西岸北部的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 16:25:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-erect-west-bank-outpost-others-attack-palestinians-in-separate-incident/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfb721d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长：政府有关国内问题的决定非法通过，必须重新考虑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-govt-decisions-on-domestic-issues-were-illegally-passed-must-be-reconsidered/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfbdcf70000</link><description>几项政府私营部门决议的通过没有适当的专业和法律基础，甚至存在法律障碍。代表总检察长发出的一封信命令政府在额外审议中重新考虑这些问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 16:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-govt-decisions-on-domestic-issues-were-illegally-passed-must-be-reconsidered/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfbdcf70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列指控哈马斯关系后，约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人担心近东救济工程处关闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/cutting-off-aid-will-hurt-many-people-west-bank-palestinians-fear-unrwa-closure/0000018d-98af-db74-a1ef-dbef17660000</link><description>该联合国机构为约旦河西岸约 87 万巴勒斯坦人提供服务，运营着 96 所学校和 43 个初级医疗机构。巴勒斯坦人担心如果该机构的资金不恢复将会发生什么</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 15:50:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/cutting-off-aid-will-hurt-many-people-west-bank-palestinians-fear-unrwa-closure/0000018d-98af-db74-a1ef-dbef17660000</guid></item><item><title>庆祝哈马斯，针对犹太人：在埃尔多安的土耳其，加沙战争营造了一种危险的气氛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/celebrating-hamas-targeting-jews-in-turkey-the-gaza-war-is-triggering-a-dangerous-mood/0000018d-985e-db74-a1ef-db5e069c0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日大屠杀以来，土耳其发生了一系列反以色列抗议和事件，这些抗议和事件有时不符合逻辑，但显然是受到总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 信息的启发</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 15:49:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/celebrating-hamas-targeting-jews-in-turkey-the-gaza-war-is-triggering-a-dangerous-mood/0000018d-985e-db74-a1ef-db5e069c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的经济表现相当不错。那么，是什么在吞噬穆迪呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-economy-is-doing-pretty-well-so-whats-eating-moodys/0000018d-9897-dc01-a9cf-9aff5f0a0000</link><description>穆迪下调以色列信用评级的原因只有一件事：不确定性——而且不仅仅是加沙战争的不确定性。政府的反应不是倾听，而是愤怒和空洞的保证</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 14:44:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-economy-is-doing-pretty-well-so-whats-eating-moodys/0000018d-9897-dc01-a9cf-9aff5f0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府将在超级碗期间投放广告呼吁释放人质父亲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-to-run-ads-calling-for-release-of-hostage-fathers-in-u-s-during-super-bowl/0000018d-984e-db74-a1ef-db4e865d0000</link><description>这些广告包括电视、广播和广告牌广告，总理办公室称这些广告的观看次数已达 1000 万次，将在全国观看超级碗比赛时在美国媒体上播放</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 14:22:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-to-run-ads-calling-for-release-of-hostage-fathers-in-u-s-during-super-bowl/0000018d-984e-db74-a1ef-db4e865d0000</guid></item><item><title>官员称，如果以色列推进拉法，埃及威胁将暂停重要和平条约</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/egypt-threatens-to-suspend-key-peace-treaty-if-israel-pushes-into-rafah-officials-say/0000018d-97e0-d443-a19f-fff1e5c50000</link><description>埃及官员担心，以色列对拉法的军事进攻（据称这是击败哈马斯所必需的）将给埃及带来灾难性的人道主义局势和可能的难民危机</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 11:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/egypt-threatens-to-suspend-key-peace-treaty-if-israel-pushes-into-rafah-officials-say/0000018d-97e0-d443-a19f-fff1e5c50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列借战争掩护，计划在东耶路撒冷修建犹太人新社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/under-the-cover-of-war-israel-is-moving-to-build-a-new-jewish-neighborhood-in-east-jlem/0000018d-9786-d9cc-a5cd-f7be43b10000</link><description>Nofei Rachel 是计划在东耶路撒冷为犹太人增加 3,000 个新住宅单元的四个街区之一。近年来，司法部已成为推进这些犹太社区建设计划的关键参与者</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 11:23:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/under-the-cover-of-war-israel-is-moving-to-build-a-new-jewish-neighborhood-in-east-jlem/0000018d-9786-d9cc-a5cd-f7be43b10000</guid></item><item><title>警方逮捕了著名的以色列作家，抗议释放哈马斯扣押的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-esteemed-israeli-author-at-protest-for-release-of-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018d-97b3-d57f-a1ef-bfbf3d210000</link><description>以色列作家兼编辑奥娜·库辛 (Orna Coussin) 表示，在特拉维夫的一次示威活动中，抗议者与警察之间爆发肢体冲突，库辛的朋友遭到暴力袭击，她赶紧向朋友伸出援手。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 11:07:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-esteemed-israeli-author-at-protest-for-release-of-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018d-97b3-d57f-a1ef-bfbf3d210000</guid></item><item><title>与无意识对话：以色列人在手术期间减少谵妄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-11/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-startup-making-communication-with-patients-under-anesthesia-possible/0000018d-97b1-d443-a19f-ffb1711f0000</link><description>以色列公司 EyeControl 开发了一种设备，可以帮助医疗团队与从麻醉中醒来的患者保持联系，并可能有助于减少谵妄 ■ 加沙战争加剧了对该设备的需求</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 11:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-11/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-startup-making-communication-with-patients-under-anesthesia-possible/0000018d-97b1-d443-a19f-ffb1711f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>